templates/methodology-retro.md.template
Sourcing mode: customization (per specs/00-vision-and-license.md §"Sourcing modes")
Working artifact for periodic methodology retrospectives. One file per
retro; date is the canonical key. Lands in the consumer's docs (e.g.
`<consumer>/docs/methodology-retro-YYYY-MM.md`), not in `docs/specs/` —
retros are time-bounded reflections, not durable behavioral contracts.

Cadence: run a retro every 4–6 features after methodology adoption,
or when a recurring failure mode signals the methodology itself
needs tuning. The first retro is typically the most valuable — it
surfaces the practices that broke under real load.

Cross-reference: `docs/methodology.md` §G "Living documents on every
ship" (retros are themselves living docs).

Authored: 2026-05-07
License: CC0 1.0 (templates ship CC0 per specs/00-vision-and-license.md §"License")
-->
